{
  "texts": [
    "The model's compilation stage involves configuring essential components for training.",
    "The Adam optimizer, a popular and effective optimization algorithm, is employed to fine-tune the network's weights.",
    "The categorical cross-entropy loss function quantifies the dissimilarity between predicted and actual class labels, facilitating effective learning.",
    "Furthermore, the model's performance during training is evaluated based on accuracy, which measures the proportion of correctly classified instances.",
    "The methodology used in this study involved training and testing 10 different AI models for tomato leaf disease detection."
  ]
}